						               													<description>Ultimate Soldier Reloaded is a fast paced strategic card game for 2 to 4 players. Each player commands highly trained soldiers that engage in combat against the other players. Your mission is to win three times in battle or earn four soldiers the fastest and become the Ultimate Soldier.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ultimate Soldier Reloaded (2017) is a brand new edition of the first edition Ultimate Soldier (2013), and is quite different from the original because it features upgraded artwork, all-new mechanics, and new characters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Ultimate Soldier Reloaded box comes with instructions plus 133 game cards:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     14 Soldier cards&amp;#10;     9 Weapon cards&amp;#10;     32 Training cards&amp;#10;     59 Action cards&amp;#10;     4 Intensity cards&amp;#10;     2 Sniper cards&amp;#10;     9 Special cards&amp;#10;     Reference cards&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player has their own soldiers, which they'll use to engage in combat against the other players. Players take turns in clockwise order, and on your turn you first draw a card from the common deck, and then do one of the following:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Play a Training card&amp;#10;     Initiate combat&amp;#10;     Discard a card&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To win, you need to get four soldier cards, or win three times in battle.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
